itle=3D"Householder transformation">Householder transformations</a>, or <a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Givens_rotation" title=3D"Givens rota=
tion">Givens rotations</a>. Each has a number of advantages and disadvantag=
es.
</p>
